description.content:
I am expert Joomla Web Developer, 10+ years experience with front-end and back-end Web Development. I did lots of customization in existing extensions (component/modules/plugins/templates) for joomla1.5, joomla2.5 and joomla3.0. Migrating old joomla1.5 websites to joomla2.5/joomla3 versions.


<========== My Joomla Skills ===========>


1.Responsive Theme development from scratch or from PSD provided.

2.Customizing and create Joomla Extensions for all Joomla versions.

3.Migrating old joomla1.5 websites to joomla2.5/joomla3 versions.

4.Speed optimizations and Clean up.


My services include.


* Full site development

* Joomla, template, extension Installation & Set up

* Customize Joomla templates 

* Joomla site Migration and Upgrade

* Joomla database migration

* Error fixing


*** Will do fast delivery 


 *** Please message me before ordering gig. So, we discuss the project before started. 

*** Price varying project to project.

reviews.comment: I had great contact with sushil, for a migration project, he was very polite and confident! i trusted the person but then when the work was deliverd, it was messy, internal links not working or pointing on the wrong article. It not usable.

seller_response.comment: Sorry, but this is not true. I delivered you the project perfectly fine and after around 1 month you came back ask me to that the work is not correct. And I asked you to please share me the issues you are getting. But I didn't get any response and you provide your rating and feedback. But please you should cordinate me the problem you facing, because when I delivered you the project all works fine.

reviews.comment: WEB EXPERT truly lives up to their name with their exceptional code expertise and impressive responsiveness! Working with them was a breeze, making the website maintenance process smooth and efficient.
Kumar has done a very good job. We will do more projects together in the future!
I am very happy with this delivery and will be doing more projects with Kumar!

reviews_snippet.comment: WEB EXPERT truly lives up to their name with their exceptional code expertise and impressive responsiveness! Working with them was a breeze, making the website maintenance process smooth and efficient.
Working with TEQTOP has been a real pleasure, deep understanding of my issue, delivered on time, with everything I needed

I am extremely happy with the result! The delivery came much earlier than announced and is perfect. Very good communication and everything met my expectations exactly. Sushil is a top expert in my eyes and I can absolutely recommend him!

Sushil Kumar helped me out with a difficult situation where I needed a real Joomla expert. Bluehost.com cancelled my website despite my being a loyal customer for almost 13 years. Bluehost.com support was not helpful at all but Kumar was able to the website up and running again. Would recommend Kumar to anyone needing Joomla website repairs or complete rebuilds.

This was a complicated site to create, and Sushil did a terrific job.  We had to figure out a lot design wise as there were so many areas that needed to be created. He was able to make the changes with ease once we figured out the design, look and palette
